Usage: set_advanced_package_options [-help] -reset | {[-tool_path <string>] [{-net_mapping_file <string> }] }

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-net_mapping_file <string>           # <def_name pkg_name two column format>
                                     # (string, optional)
-reset                               # <clear all settings> (bool, optional)
-tool_path <string>                  # <bin folder of package analysis tool>
                                     # (string, optional)